title: #92Noon! 10a Hour 3/4 - Combine/Russo/News
description: The hour begins by pondering the value of speed in the NFL, and how fast 40 times at the Combine don't often equate to productive NFL careers....Russo Radio from out east as the Wild ended a losing streak and face Buffalo tonight....NDN to cap off the middle stretch
